## ğŸ’³ Detailed Payment Flow (BOT)

### Deposit Process:

```
1. User: /deposit 50
2. Bot: "ĞŸĞµÑ€ĞµĞ²ĞµĞ´Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğµ 50 USDT Ğ½Ğ° Ğ°Ğ´Ñ€ĞµÑ: 0x123..."
3. Bot: [QR Code image]
4. Bot: "ĞĞ¶Ğ¸Ğ´Ğ°ĞµĞ¼ Ğ¿Ğ¾ÑÑ‚ÑƒĞ¿Ğ»ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğµ..."
5. System: Monitors blockchain
6. Bot: "âœ… ĞŸĞ¾ÑÑ‚ÑƒĞ¿Ğ¸Ğ»Ğ¾ 50 USDT! Ğ‘Ğ°Ğ»Ğ°Ğ½Ñ: 100 USDT"

```

### Withdrawal Process:

```
1. User: /withdraw 0x456... 30
2. Bot: "ĞŸĞ¾Ğ´Ñ‚Ğ²ĞµÑ€Ğ´Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğµ Ğ²Ñ‹Ğ²Ğ¾Ğ´ 30 USDT Ğ½Ğ° 0x456...?"
3. User: Confirms
4. Bot: "ĞĞ±Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ°Ñ‚Ñ‹Ğ²Ğ°ĞµĞ¼..."
5. System: Sends transaction
6. Bot: "âœ… ĞÑ‚Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ°Ğ²Ğ»ĞµĞ½Ğ¾! TxHash: 0x789..."

```

### Bot Commands Structure:

```jsx
// ĞÑĞ½Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ½Ñ‹Ğµ ĞºĞ¾Ğ¼Ğ°Ğ½Ğ´Ñ‹
/start - Welcome message + registration
/help - List of commands
/balance - Show current balance
/deposit [amount] - Generate deposit address
/withdraw [address] [amount] - Withdraw USDT
/history - Last 10 transactions
/support - Contact support

// ĞĞ´Ğ¼Ğ¸Ğ½ÑĞºĞ¸Ğµ ĞºĞ¾Ğ¼Ğ°Ğ½Ğ´Ñ‹
/admin - Enter admin mode
/add_case [name] [price] - Add new case
/add_prize [case_id] [name] [rarity] - Add prize
/stats - Show system statistics
/users - User management
/set_balance [user_id] [amount] - Set user balance

```

