## ğŸ’³ Detailed Payment Flow (BOT)

### Deposit Process (Inline):

```
1. User clicks "ğŸ’³ Deposit" button
2. Bot shows amount selection buttons [10$][25$][50$][Custom]
3. User selects amount or enters custom
4. Bot generates address + shows QR code button
5. User clicks "ğŸ“± Show QR Code"
6. Bot shows QR image + "ğŸ”„ Check Status" button
7. User pays, clicks check status
8. Bot: "âœ… Received 50 USDT! Balance updated"

```

### Withdrawal Process (Inline):

```
1. User clicks "ğŸ’¸ Withdraw" button
2. Bot shows amount buttons [10$][25$][50$][Max][Custom]
3. User selects amount
4. Bot asks for address with [ğŸ“ Enter][ğŸ“š Saved][ğŸ“± QR Scan]
5. User provides address
6. Bot shows confirmation with [âœ… Confirm][âŒ Cancel]
7. User confirms
8. Bot: "Processing..." â†’ "âœ… Sent! Hash: 0x123..."

```

